{"title":"BlackHeart Bike Co Rolls Out the Gravel Ti, its New Titanium Gravel Bike","link":"https://bikerumor.com/blackheart-bike-co-gravel-ti-bike/","date":1742313600000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-Hero-e1742237051911.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"702\" alt=\"(Photos / BlackHeart Bike Co.)\" /></p>\n<p>Truckee, California’s<a href=\"https://blackheartbikeco.com/\"> BlackHeart Cycle Co</a> has released its latest titanium offering. The new Gravel Ti takes its DNA from Blackheart’s Road Ti and Gravel AL, blended together to make a modern gravel bike with the timeless aesthetics of titanium.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-second-pic.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-second-pic.webp\" alt=\"BlackHeart Bike Co New Gravel Ti second pic\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-second-pic.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-second-pic-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-second-pic-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-second-pic-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-second-pic-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-second-pic-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / BlackHeart Bike Co.)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-first-pic.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-first-pic.webp\" alt=\"BlackHeart Bike Co New Gravel Ti first pic\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-first-pic.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-first-pic-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-first-pic-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-first-pic-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-first-pic-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-first-pic-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-curved-seat-stays.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"1279\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-curved-seat-stays.webp\" alt=\"BlackHeart Bike Co New Gravel Ti curved seat stays\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-curved-seat-stays.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-curved-seat-stays-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-curved-seat-stays-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-curved-seat-stays-768x767.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Gravel Ti is fabricated using 3/2.5 double-butted titanium tubing. It sports elegantly curved seat stays designed to smooth out the ride. A Kammtail downtube with a tapered, ovalized top tube, and internal routing, makes for a super clean look.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-T47-bb-e1742237301645.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"898\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-T47-bb-e1742237301645.webp\" alt=\"BlackHeart Bike Co New Gravel Ti T47 bb\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-T47-bb-e1742237301645.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-T47-bb-e1742237301645-297x208.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-T47-bb-e1742237301645-120x84.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-T47-bb-e1742237301645-768x539.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Gravel Ti is ready for a 1x or 2x drivetrain using electronic drivetrains and 1x only for mechanical drivetrains.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-round-seatpost-e1742237430372.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"892\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-round-seatpost-e1742237430372.webp\" alt=\"BlackHeart Bike Co New Gravel Ti round seatpost\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-round-seatpost-e1742237430372.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-round-seatpost-e1742237430372-297x207.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-round-seatpost-e1742237430372-120x84.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-round-seatpost-e1742237430372-768x535.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The frame comes with a UDH rear derailleur hanger, a T47 bottom bracket, and a round 31.6mm seat post, to maximize parts options. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-evne-fork.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-evne-fork.webp\" alt=\"BlackHeart Bike Co New Gravel Ti evne fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-evne-fork.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-evne-fork-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-evne-fork-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-evne-fork-768x768.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-intgrated-barstem-e1742237357492.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1279\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-intgrated-barstem-e1742237357492.webp\" alt=\"BlackHeart Bike Co New Gravel Ti intgrated bar:stem\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-intgrated-barstem-e1742237357492.webp 1279w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-intgrated-barstem-e1742237357492-297x232.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-intgrated-barstem-e1742237357492-120x94.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-intgrated-barstem-e1742237357492-768x600.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The frameset will come with an ENVE In-route Gravel carbon fork, along with an FSA ACR headset. This gives the customer the option to select a standard non-integrated stem and bar combo. Or they can upgrade to the BlackHeart one-piece carbon bar/stem, or ENVE in-route headset and bar/stem combo to match the fork.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frame-drive-side-e1742237180169.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"678\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frame-drive-side-e1742237180169.webp\" alt=\"BlackHeart Bike Co New Gravel Ti frame drive side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frame-drive-side-e1742237180169.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frame-drive-side-e1742237180169-297x157.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frame-drive-side-e1742237180169-120x64.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frame-drive-side-e1742237180169-768x407.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frameset-front-side-e1742237479805.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"642\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frameset-front-side-e1742237479805.webp\" alt=\"BlackHeart Bike Co New Gravel Ti frameset front side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frameset-front-side-e1742237479805.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frameset-front-side-e1742237479805-297x149.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frameset-front-side-e1742237479805-120x60.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frameset-front-side-e1742237479805-768x385.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Titanium will never rust or corrode making it a “lifetime” frame material. Furthermore, it’s also highly recyclable, if that time ever comes.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frameset-e1742237532396.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"565\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frameset-e1742237532396.webp\" alt=\"BlackHeart Bike Co New Gravel Ti frameset\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frameset-e1742237532396.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frameset-e1742237532396-297x131.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frameset-e1742237532396-120x53.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-New-Gravel-Ti-frameset-e1742237532396-768x339.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>According to BlackHeart, these frames are manufactured in a “premiere Asian titanium factory” and carry a lifetime warranty for the original owner against manufacturing defects. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Gravel Ti Retail &amp; Detail</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $3,299 (frameset: frame, ENVE fork, seatpost, seatpost clamp, headset, thru-axles, and spare SRAM UDH)</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>BlackHeart one-piece carbon bar/stem can be added for $400</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Customizable builds start at $5,199</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Custom fork paint available starting at $200</li>\n\n\n\n<li>8 sizes fit riders from ~5’0″ to ~6’7″</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Weight: <br />Frameset: 1890d (size 56)<br />Complete build: 19-22lbs</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The new BlackHeart Gravel Ti is available now for pre-order at the link below, or through their dealer network, for a Summer 2025 delivery. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://blackheartbikeco.com/\" target=\"_blank\">BlackheartBikeCo.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/blackheart-bike-co-gravel-ti-bike/\">BlackHeart Bike Co Rolls Out the Gravel Ti, its New Titanium Gravel Bike</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"8b4159e88bed1ddbd289f6437378a32299d7f561f0f5f1db8a0054272022192b","category":"Cycling"}